    "name": "Easy Red 2",
    "steam_appid": 1324780,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i><strong>我们将在30秒后进行抢滩登陆！时刻警惕！愿你们能活着迎接胜利！</strong></i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《Easy Red 2》是一款具有高战术性、写实、高历史还原度的二战射击游戏，专注于大规模、沉浸式的战斗，让你身临其境于血雨腥风的二战前线。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>指挥你的小队，协调各兵种协同作战，在以真实历史战场为蓝本的广袤战场上浴血奋战。你可以在单人战役对抗人机，也可以与其他真人玩家展开比拼。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >全球性的战役</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在世界上各个二战战场展开战斗。《Easy Red 2》本体包含 6 个内容丰富的战役：</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>安齐奥战役</strong>：1944年，轴心国和盟军在意大利中部的广袤平原展开了一场持续数月的残酷血腥的僵局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>卡西诺山战役</strong>：一场著名的山地战役，盟军对德军的古斯塔夫防线发动了多次战略进攻。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>突尼斯战役</strong>：1943年，德军在北非战场的最后之战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>燧发枪行动</strong>：发生在夸贾林环礁和罗伊纳穆尔岛的马绍尔群岛：1944年初，美国陆军太平洋部队和海军陆战队分别行动，夺取了被大日本帝国占据的诸个太平洋岛屿。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>马金环礁战役</strong>：这场战役与著名的塔拉瓦战役同时发生，美国陆军太平洋部队在1943年末攻占马金环礁，进一步实施了他们的太平洋跳岛行动。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>科斯岛战役</strong>：一座鲜为人知的希腊岛屿，曾被受同盟国支持的意大利军队占领，德军于1943年重新夺回了该岛。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纵览这些战役，它们包含了<strong>超过75个独一无二的任务关卡</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/54a40dd43285ce45247af1ed4c09e2b0.poster.avif?t=1769186261\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/54a40dd43285ce45247af1ed4c09e2b0.webm?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/54a40dd43285ce45247af1ed4c09e2b0.mp4?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Easy Red 2也提供了其他二战著名战役作为DLC，涵盖从 <i>东线战场的斯大林格勒</i>，<i>西线战场的诺曼底登陆</i>，甚至是二战东方主战场的<i>淞沪会战以及南京保卫战</i>。 这些战役DLC呈现了史实的载具，武器，制服以及共计包含了<strong>80个任务关卡。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >持续不断地更新优化</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Easy Red 2》一直在不断更新优化。无论是人机的全面改进、动画系统的更新，还是新增免费载具、武器或制服，随着时间的推移，游戏定会持续发展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沉浸式战争氛围</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《Easy Red 2》中，你将成为战场上的一名普通士兵，在二战的不同战役中进行战斗，体验历史上真实的战事变动以及战场氛围。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/6e0e9c0924986c0678c58d59553804c3.poster.avif?t=1769186261\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/6e0e9c0924986c0678c58d59553804c3.webm?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/6e0e9c0924986c0678c58d59553804c3.mp4?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在战场上，你<i>并非</i>所谓的超级战士------你必须在枪林弹雨和血雨腥风的人间炼狱中艰难前行。正因如此，你并非能够一直存活到最终的胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >小队指挥机制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >没有人会孤军奋战。《Easy Red 2》中，你可以操控由不同兵种组成的小队：队长、通信兵、医疗兵、机枪手等等------每个角色都拥有独特的技能，说不定能让你扭转战局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/2784cd43cc6b5880a8cc738e70a2486b.poster.avif?t=1769186261\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/2784cd43cc6b5880a8cc738e70a2486b.webm?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/2784cd43cc6b5880a8cc738e70a2486b.mp4?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >机械化战争</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶二战时期的著名坦克驰骋各个战场，包含了装甲等效、弹道模拟和各个乘员独立操控等机制。请注意，如果乘员阵亡，载具的某些功能也可能随之失效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/042d5737e5e95cc53db044e7dbb97156.poster.avif?t=1769186261\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/042d5737e5e95cc53db044e7dbb97156.webm?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/042d5737e5e95cc53db044e7dbb97156.mp4?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >包含了众多著名的二战载具：<strong>M4谢尔曼坦克, 威利斯吉普车, 丘吉尔步兵坦克, 豹式坦克以及虎式坦克</strong>。除了地上跑的，当然还有天上飞的： <strong>喷火战斗机, P-51野马战斗机, P-40战鹰战斗机, P-38闪电战斗机, F4F野猫战斗机以及Bf 109战斗机。</strong>游戏中当然远远不止这些！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >可破坏的建筑以及环境</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战场环礁并非一成不变。在战斗过程中，森林会被夷为焦土，防御工事会被摧毁，建筑物会轰然倒塌等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/4d8278d1ecc6c0b7891358a3c28105d8.poster.avif?t=1769186261\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/4d8278d1ecc6c0b7891358a3c28105d8.webm?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/4d8278d1ecc6c0b7891358a3c28105d8.mp4?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多人模式</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可与你的好友进行PVP竞赛或者多人合作通关战役。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你也可以使用游戏本体自带的关卡任务、Steam创意工坊或你自己创建的自定义任务来进行PVP亦或是PVE。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多人模式中你可以加入好友的小队或者只使用自己的小队。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随时随地，随心所欲地畅享多人模式吧！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/02935b4892aea474b9bd904b4e4cbb2b.poster.avif?t=1769186261\" width=720 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/02935b4892aea474b9bd904b4e4cbb2b.webm?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/02935b4892aea474b9bd904b4e4cbb2b.mp4?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >支持模组</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >制作并分享<strong>自己打造的独特战役或关卡场景</strong>, 地图, 以及其他自定义内容都可以通过 <strong>非常方便的</strong>游戏自带的地图和任务编辑器来实现！<br>你还可以使用专用的<strong>Modding SDK</strong>来制作<strong>更多模组</strong>。<br>在<strong>Steam 创意工坊</strong>分享你的模组，且你可以通过<strong>战役模式</strong>或是<strong>多人模式</strong>来游玩你的模组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/c2271fff3a1698b8042a83296009d1c7.poster.avif?t=1769186261\" width=614 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/c2271fff3a1698b8042a83296009d1c7.webm?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1324780/extras/c2271fff3a1698b8042a83296009d1c7.mp4?t=1769186261\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>三...二...一！放下登陆艇挡板！</i></h2>",
